channel.title: El Server (Beta) | Bug Testers Join!
channel.description:
Welcome to El Server. This is a server I have been working on. Its not the best. I am currently new to code a [PI] server. I am looking for a couple of people to test for bugs as there is probably many. Rewards will be giving to those to find bug that would like to stay on the server. Rewards giving after beta is over.
If you would like to be a bug tester follow the link below: [url=http://www.elserver.x10host.com/home.html]http://http://www.elserver.x10host.com/home.html[/url]
Thank you your time, Hope to see you soon.
